# RQ-53-10-01-184: Predictive Repair Scheduling

## Requirement Statement
CAOS shall predict optimal timing for nose cone repairs based on condition monitoring data.

## Rationale
Optimize maintenance scheduling to minimize unscheduled downtime while maintaining safety margins.

## Acceptance Criteria
- Predict repair needs 500 FH in advance
- Accuracy: > 80% correct predictions
- Integration with maintenance planning system
- Automatic work order generation

## Compliance Status
Predictive model in development

## Traceability
Parent: RQ-53-10-01-180 (Digital Twin)
